	<h1>Questions, Feature Requests, Reporting Errors</h1>
	
	<p>
		We welcome feedback. Many of the features on Memverse were implemented in response to feedback from users. 
		The best place for asking questions, requesting new features, and reporting bugs is our support forum. 
		We monitor it daily and there are often users online who can give a quick answer. 
		You can either click on the GetSatisfaction icon below or the black 'Feedback' tab on the right.
	</p>
	
